title: Rigmar Radio Karaoke Part 1A3
description:
Please read the CSV Text file for the full listings for Part 1.  Each torrent contains 300 plus tracks in CDG+MP3 format correctly tagged and file named for playback from a Laptop PC or Mac.   This is a professional Karaoke collection and now includes multiple choice Karaoke Label selection for the more popular songs.

This is the 3rd torrent in the Part 1 series which features the letter A.

Import the CSV Text file into Excell or the Speadsheet of your choice, select the columns you wish to keep and sort by Artist (default) or by Song Title, add a header and footer, perhaps a page number and print your own Karaoke Book for each part.

The whole collection will be yours by late January 2016 and you will require at least 300GB of storage space to use it.

From now on they will be listed as Rigmar Radio Karaoke Part # Letter # where # equals the Part Number and Letter number of the download.  ie:

Rigmar Radio Karaoke Part 1A14
Rigmar Radio Karaoke Part 1A15
Rigmar Radio Karaoke Part 2B
Rigmar Radio Karaoke Part 2B1 and so on until we reach Part ##Z## and the end of this years collection.  Enjoy and PLEASE help me seed as I have not got the upload bandwidth to seed every part (who has??) and unseeded parts will slow me down as I will have to return to them until the peers have it all and move on.
